1
00:01:43,560 --> 00:01:44,070
Brother Fan

2
00:01:44,150 --> 00:01:44,760
Brother Fan

3
00:01:44,760 --> 00:01:46,230
You guys aren't dead?

4
00:01:46,400 --> 00:01:47,310
You're the one who's dead, you bastard.

5
00:01:49,120 --> 00:01:51,150
It's not that easy to kill us off.

6
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:54,920
You guys go up and call Big Brother out.

7
00:01:55,230 --> 00:01:57,150
Let's get out of this hellhole together.

8
00:01:57,280 --> 00:01:57,920
Wait a minute.

9
00:01:58,590 --> 00:02:00,510
Never mind the risk if we get caught,

10
00:02:00,870 --> 00:02:02,200
Big Brother definitely won't leave.

11
00:02:03,230 --> 00:02:05,150
Then you guys just trick him into coming out.

12
00:02:05,590 --> 00:02:06,760
Tie him up and drag him along if you have to.

13
00:02:07,150 --> 00:02:07,790
Go, hurry.

14
00:02:08,480 --> 00:02:09,480
Alright, alright.

15
00:02:10,840 --> 00:02:11,480
Hurry up!

16
00:02:16,470 --> 00:02:17,520
Since you're back,

17
00:02:17,750 --> 00:02:18,680
why don't you come inside?

18
00:02:21,000 --> 00:02:21,870
Ma the Tigress.

19
00:02:25,150 --> 00:02:26,520
These stairs are so steep.

20
00:02:26,910 --> 00:02:28,030
I'm exhausted.

21
00:02:28,030 --> 00:02:29,120
Just resting a bit.

22
00:02:32,560 --> 00:02:33,280
Ma the Tigress...

23
00:02:35,280 --> 00:02:37,360
I brought Scarface back to you.

24
00:02:37,750 --> 00:02:40,430
He is your right-hand man, after all.

25
00:02:40,840 --> 00:02:42,030
If he were to die out there,

26
00:02:42,360 --> 00:02:45,240
word would spread that you're disloyal.

27
00:02:47,280 --> 00:02:48,470
It's good that you're back safe.

28
00:02:48,840 --> 00:02:49,680
For the next couple of days,

29
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:51,030
you don't have to do any work.

30
00:02:51,710 --> 00:02:52,630
Just rest up.

31
00:02:55,800 --> 00:02:56,560
Let's go.

32
00:02:59,750 --> 00:03:00,400
Let's go.

33
00:03:02,150 --> 00:03:02,910
Let's go.

34
00:03:10,590 --> 00:03:11,520
Slow down, slow down.

35
00:03:23,520 --> 00:03:25,590
Boss Xiu Gu, business is booming.

36
00:03:25,800 --> 00:03:27,560
It's your Commander Qin whose business is booming.

37
00:03:33,080 --> 00:03:34,280
This is the Huo Family residence.

38
00:03:34,630 --> 00:03:35,590
Don't you recognize it?

39
00:03:36,150 --> 00:03:37,080
Sitting here blocking the door.

40
00:03:37,750 --> 00:03:38,560
Sorry about that.

41
00:03:38,910 --> 00:03:40,000
I'm waiting for someone here.

42
00:03:40,520 --> 00:03:41,240
Sorry.

43
00:03:44,710 --> 00:03:46,120
Are you waiting for our Young Master?

44
00:03:46,910 --> 00:03:47,590
No.

45
00:03:48,800 --> 00:03:50,520
Our Huo Family, in this town,

46
00:03:50,520 --> 00:03:52,360
is one of the most prominent families.

47
00:03:52,630 --> 00:03:53,310
Who are you waiting for?

48
00:03:53,520 --> 00:03:54,310
Tell me.

49
00:03:54,560 --> 00:03:55,590
Maybe I know them.

50
00:03:56,590 --> 00:03:58,240
I'm waiting for the boss across the street.

51
00:04:00,120 --> 00:04:00,870
Uncle Dong.

52
00:04:02,630 --> 00:04:05,190
Isn't there a Boss Fan across the street?

53
00:04:06,560 --> 00:04:07,870
Oh, Boss Fan.

54
00:04:08,520 --> 00:04:09,120
Yes.

55
00:04:09,310 --> 00:04:10,030
You are...

56
00:04:10,400 --> 00:04:11,400
I'm his wife.

57
00:04:11,840 --> 00:04:13,590
You are Boss Fan's wife?

58
00:04:14,120 --> 00:04:16,560
Our Young Master and Boss Fan,

59
00:04:16,560 --> 00:04:17,590
have a very good relationship.

60
00:04:17,840 --> 00:04:19,280
They are sworn brothers.

61
00:04:20,800 --> 00:04:21,710
Then do you know,

62
00:04:21,710 --> 00:04:23,000
where he has gone now?

63
00:04:24,390 --> 00:04:25,720
Come inside and have some tea first.

64
00:04:25,920 --> 00:04:27,510
When our Young Master Huo returns in a bit,

65
00:04:27,680 --> 00:04:29,750
he should know where Boss Fan is.

66
00:04:30,830 --> 00:04:31,630
Let's go.

67
00:04:32,040 --> 00:04:33,000
Later when Boss Fan comes back,

68
00:04:33,000 --> 00:04:34,240
and tells our Young Master Huo,

69
00:04:34,430 --> 00:04:35,630
that we didn't treat you well...

70
00:04:36,630 --> 00:04:38,070
Why is it less each time?

71
00:04:38,310 --> 00:04:39,430
Can't you see for yourself?

72
00:04:39,560 --> 00:04:40,600
Then I'll impose on you.

73
00:04:40,600 --> 00:04:41,120
Please.

74
00:04:41,120 --> 00:04:42,160
I advise you one thing.

75
00:04:42,680 --> 00:04:44,430
Work hard for Commander Qin.

76
00:04:44,750 --> 00:04:45,800
Opposing him,

77
00:04:46,120 --> 00:04:47,190
won't end well.

78
00:04:48,310 --> 00:04:49,040
Officer.

79
00:04:49,390 --> 00:04:50,240
Officer, Officer.

80
00:04:50,680 --> 00:04:52,160
Don't worry about this.

81
00:04:52,270 --> 00:04:54,270
We will definitely for Commander Qin,

82
00:04:54,390 --> 00:04:55,800
do our work properly.

83
00:04:56,270 --> 00:04:57,310
You saw it too.

84
00:04:57,310 --> 00:04:58,430
Business is hard to do.

85
00:04:58,600 --> 00:04:59,600
But these accounts,

86
00:04:59,870 --> 00:05:01,190
are absolutely real.

87
00:05:02,480 --> 00:05:04,360
We were ambushed by government troops this time.

88
00:05:04,430 --> 00:05:05,950
Brothers, you've worked hard.

89
00:05:06,270 --> 00:05:07,800
Come, drink a bowl.

90
00:05:07,950 --> 00:05:09,510
Boss Ma, you've worked hard.

91
00:05:09,510 --> 00:05:10,830
Cheers, cheers.

92
00:05:12,830 --> 00:05:14,070
The world is cold and fickle.

93
00:05:14,360 --> 00:05:15,870
We try to make a living for ourselves,

94
00:05:16,040 --> 00:05:18,070
but the troops try to exterminate us.

95
00:05:18,310 --> 00:05:20,510
We and the troops are sworn enemies.

96
00:05:20,920 --> 00:05:21,950
Have another bowl.

97
00:05:22,120 --> 00:05:23,950
Sworn enemies!

98
00:05:23,950 --> 00:05:25,510
Cheers.

99
00:05:30,630 --> 00:05:31,560
Scarface.

100
00:05:31,870 --> 00:05:33,120
You served well in protecting me this time.

101
00:05:33,510 --> 00:05:34,750
Reward: one roast chicken.

102
00:05:40,120 --> 00:05:41,240
Advisor Fan.

103
00:05:41,950 --> 00:05:43,830
Saving Scarface is merit upon merit.

104
00:05:44,430 --> 00:05:45,630
Also rewarded with a roast chicken.

105
00:05:46,600 --> 00:05:47,630
I dare not accept.

106
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:49,600
Good.

107
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:52,360
This meal is to calm everyone's nerves.

108
00:05:52,720 --> 00:05:55,190
Eat and drink your fill, regain your might.

109
00:05:55,720 --> 00:05:56,600
Dig in.

110
00:06:08,270 --> 00:06:09,630
Why did you come back again?

111
00:06:16,310 --> 00:06:18,070
Ma Gang, Ma Gang.

112
00:06:18,390 --> 00:06:20,070
Ma Gang, Ma Gang.

113
00:06:24,120 --> 00:06:25,950
Rise up, rise up.

114
00:06:27,750 --> 00:06:29,430
United in heart and effort.

115
00:06:31,430 --> 00:06:33,160
Create glory again.

116
00:06:34,870 --> 00:06:36,600
Ma Gang, Ma Gang.

117
00:06:36,600 --> 00:06:38,160
Rise up, rise up.

118
00:06:38,310 --> 00:06:39,830
United in heart and effort.

119
00:06:40,000 --> 00:06:42,000
Create glory again.

120
00:06:42,480 --> 00:06:44,950
Good.

121
00:06:45,120 --> 00:06:47,190
Come, brothers, let's have a drink.

122
00:06:47,360 --> 00:06:48,390
Come, cheers, come.

123
00:06:57,920 --> 00:06:58,920
Where is that woman from just now?

124
00:07:00,000 --> 00:07:00,830
Which woman?

125
00:07:00,920 --> 00:07:02,270
I saw you take her inside.

126
00:07:03,040 --> 00:07:05,120
Do you think our Young Master Huo

127
00:07:05,240 --> 00:07:06,950
only associates with you?

128
00:07:07,510 --> 00:07:08,160
What of it?

129
00:07:08,560 --> 00:07:09,310
Regretting it now?

130
00:07:09,600 --> 00:07:11,160
It's too late.

131
00:07:12,270 --> 00:07:13,190
Mrs. Fan!

132
00:07:13,430 --> 00:07:14,390
Mrs. Fan, come out quickly!

133
00:07:14,390 --> 00:07:15,360
Shut your mouth!

134
00:07:15,680 --> 00:07:16,510
Xiu Gu.

135
00:07:16,920 --> 00:07:18,480
What do you think you're doing?

136
00:07:19,870 --> 00:07:21,830
Uncle Dong, control your daughter.

137
00:07:21,830 --> 00:07:22,600
All right, all right.

138
00:07:22,680 --> 00:07:24,680
Don't think just because Commander Qin protects you now,

139
00:07:24,830 --> 00:07:26,600
that I can't sue you for trespassing on a private residence

140
00:07:26,830 --> 00:07:27,870
and drag you to the authorities.

141
00:07:28,360 --> 00:07:30,000
I know, I know.

142
00:07:30,190 --> 00:07:32,160
You damn girl, are you crazy?

143
00:07:32,160 --> 00:07:32,830
Go home.

144
00:07:33,000 --> 00:07:33,920
Mrs. Fan.

145
00:07:33,920 --> 00:07:35,190
We're going back.

146
00:07:39,600 --> 00:07:40,390
Mrs. Fan.

147
00:07:40,630 --> 00:07:42,750
I didn't know you would be gracing us with your presence today,

148
00:07:43,070 --> 00:07:45,750
so I've only prepared a simple meal.

149
00:07:46,120 --> 00:07:47,560
Please fill your stomach first.

150
00:07:47,800 --> 00:07:48,390
Later,

151
00:07:48,390 --> 00:07:49,630
our Young Master

152
00:07:49,800 --> 00:07:51,190
will host a proper welcome banquet for you.

153
00:07:51,830 --> 00:07:52,630
Thank you.

154
00:07:53,000 --> 00:07:53,950
But right now,

155
00:07:53,950 --> 00:07:54,800
I just want to quickly see

156
00:07:54,800 --> 00:07:56,120
the Boss Fan you mentioned.

157
00:07:59,040 --> 00:08:00,480
So this is Mrs. Fan?

158
00:08:02,240 --> 00:08:03,190
Boss Fan

159
00:08:03,190 --> 00:08:04,870
is truly a lucky man.

160
00:08:06,510 --> 00:08:07,830
My surname is Huo.

161
00:08:08,040 --> 00:08:09,800
I am a business partner of Boss Fan.

162
00:08:10,680 --> 00:08:11,510
Young Master Huo.

163
00:08:11,630 --> 00:08:12,560
To tell you the truth,

164
00:08:12,750 --> 00:08:14,950
Boss Fan was doing business here,

165
00:08:14,950 --> 00:08:16,480
but he was set up by villains

166
00:08:16,630 --> 00:08:19,310
and offended the local Commander Qin.

167
00:08:19,510 --> 00:08:22,190
He is currently out laying low.

168
00:08:23,560 --> 00:08:25,000
Then do you know

169
00:08:25,480 --> 00:08:27,160
exactly where he is right now?

170
00:08:27,750 --> 00:08:29,390
I am also sending people to look for him.

171
00:08:32,120 --> 00:08:33,070
Since that is the case,

172
00:08:33,480 --> 00:08:34,630
I won't trouble you any longer.

173
00:08:35,000 --> 00:08:36,120
I will go find him myself.

174
00:08:41,840 --> 00:08:43,240
You are a stranger to this place;

175
00:08:43,240 --> 00:08:44,600
where would you even look?

176
00:08:44,600 --> 00:08:47,510
You should just stay here with peace of mind.

177
00:08:47,840 --> 00:08:48,720
As soon as there is news,

178
00:08:48,720 --> 00:08:50,440
I will send someone to notify you.

179
00:08:51,390 --> 00:08:52,750
Besides,

180
00:08:53,440 --> 00:08:54,960
if Commander Qin finds out

181
00:08:54,960 --> 00:08:57,030
that you are Boss Fan's wife,

182
00:08:57,630 --> 00:08:59,480
I fear it could lead to a fatal disaster.

183
00:09:00,600 --> 00:09:02,360
What kind of trouble did he get into?

184
00:09:02,960 --> 00:09:04,030
Well,

185
00:09:04,360 --> 00:09:05,720
it's a long story.

186
00:09:06,840 --> 00:09:09,150
Have men wait outside.

187
00:09:09,390 --> 00:09:12,360
Try to satisfy all of Mrs. Fan's needs.

188
00:09:13,000 --> 00:09:13,720
Young Master Huo,

189
00:09:13,720 --> 00:09:15,720
please don't stand on ceremony with me.

190
00:09:16,080 --> 00:09:17,600
Given my friendship with Boss Fan,

191
00:09:17,750 --> 00:09:19,910
you can completely treat this place as your own home.

192
00:09:21,440 --> 00:09:22,720
Have a good meal first.

193
00:09:22,910 --> 00:09:24,790
I have matters to attend to, so I'll take my leave.

194
00:09:28,320 --> 00:09:29,120
Young Master Huo!

195
00:09:29,270 --> 00:09:30,360
There's no need for all this trouble.

196
00:09:33,480 --> 00:09:34,600
What are you doing?

197
00:09:35,840 --> 00:09:37,270
Bandits have been rampant lately.

198
00:09:37,510 --> 00:09:39,630
This is to protect your safety, Mrs. Fan.

199
00:09:46,750 --> 00:09:48,000
Why are you locking the door?

200
00:09:50,270 --> 00:09:52,150
Young Master Huo, Young Master Huo...

201
00:09:57,270 --> 00:09:59,600
Never mind the adjutant coming to audit,

202
00:10:00,440 --> 00:10:02,750
even if Commander Qin came with an abacus,

203
00:10:03,240 --> 00:10:04,720
he wouldn't find a thing.

204
00:10:11,390 --> 00:10:13,790
You don't care about your old man

205
00:10:13,790 --> 00:10:16,000
stealing meat from a wolf's mouth,

206
00:10:16,240 --> 00:10:19,080
but you worry about a woman you don't even know.

207
00:10:20,320 --> 00:10:21,910
If you're so capable,

208
00:10:21,910 --> 00:10:23,320
then go save her.

209
00:10:23,480 --> 00:10:24,150
You're right.

210
00:10:25,200 --> 00:10:26,390
That's exactly what I plan to do.

211
00:10:28,670 --> 00:10:30,390
Don't be crazy.

212
00:10:31,030 --> 00:10:32,080
Haven't you always

213
00:10:32,080 --> 00:10:34,150
wanted to draw a line with the Huo family

214
00:10:34,270 --> 00:10:35,510
and never deal with them again?

215
00:10:36,600 --> 00:10:38,480
Brother Fan saved me from in there.

216
00:10:39,030 --> 00:10:40,750
Now his wife has been tricked into going there.

217
00:10:40,870 --> 00:10:42,200
I can't just ignore it.

218
00:10:42,360 --> 00:10:46,000
Young Master Huo is just using his wife to threaten him.

219
00:10:46,150 --> 00:10:48,320
He won't do anything to his wife.

220
00:10:48,870 --> 00:10:50,550
If that Huo guy can't find Brother Fan,

221
00:10:50,550 --> 00:10:52,080
and wants to vent his anger?

222
00:10:57,360 --> 00:10:58,750
Brother Fan promised me

223
00:11:00,080 --> 00:11:01,870
he would tell his wife about us.

224
00:11:02,670 --> 00:11:03,790
As long as she agrees,

225
00:11:05,030 --> 00:11:06,150
he will marry me.

226
00:11:07,870 --> 00:11:08,550
What?

227
00:11:09,910 --> 00:11:12,000
You're willing to be a concubine?

228
00:11:15,630 --> 00:11:18,080
If you truly want to marry him,

229
00:11:18,240 --> 00:11:19,960
then don't save that woman.

230
00:11:20,200 --> 00:11:22,240
It'll make room for you.

231
00:11:22,870 --> 00:11:23,870
Dad.

232
00:11:24,600 --> 00:11:25,750
The state I was in when I left the Huo house,

233
00:11:25,750 --> 00:11:27,240
it's not like you didn't see it.

234
00:11:27,720 --> 00:11:28,440
Okay, okay, okay.

235
00:11:28,440 --> 00:11:29,320
Alright, alright, alright.

236
00:11:29,790 --> 00:11:31,550
About that matter,

237
00:11:31,550 --> 00:11:32,600
I was wrong.

238
00:11:33,120 --> 00:11:35,200
I... I know.

239
00:11:35,390 --> 00:11:36,910
Don't bring it up anymore.

240
00:11:46,240 --> 00:11:48,030
I'm not blaming you.

241
00:11:49,320 --> 00:11:50,870
But when I was in there,

242
00:11:51,320 --> 00:11:52,790
I still had you and Brother Fan.

243
00:11:53,600 --> 00:11:55,270
I still had hope.

244
00:11:56,630 --> 00:11:58,440
But who can she count on now?

245
00:12:04,440 --> 00:12:05,790
You really want to go save her?

246
00:12:09,670 --> 00:12:10,200
Fine.

247
00:12:10,720 --> 00:12:11,870
Then promise me,

248
00:12:12,720 --> 00:12:14,750
you'll listen to me for everything.

249
00:12:15,270 --> 00:12:16,510
This is my own business.

250
00:12:16,510 --> 00:12:17,870
You don't need to come with me.

251
00:12:18,440 --> 00:12:20,360
Your business is my business.

252
00:12:21,670 --> 00:12:23,550
Promise me you'll listen to me.

253
00:12:24,630 --> 00:12:25,240
Okay.

254
00:12:25,790 --> 00:12:26,510
I promise.

255
00:12:31,360 --> 00:12:32,440
Wait until dark.

256
00:12:39,840 --> 00:12:42,270
Everyone agreed to leave together.

257
00:12:42,720 --> 00:12:43,440
Sure, sure.

258
00:12:45,440 --> 00:12:47,600
Big Brother won't agree to it.

259
00:12:47,960 --> 00:12:48,910
He is Big Brother.

260
00:12:49,150 --> 00:12:50,360
How dare we lay a hand on him?

261
00:12:50,750 --> 00:12:51,870
The problem is he's so huge.

262
00:12:52,080 --> 00:12:53,480
How can we beat him?

263
00:12:54,510 --> 00:12:55,550
Desperate times

264
00:12:56,480 --> 00:12:58,870
call for desperate measures.

265
00:12:59,030 --> 00:13:00,870
What if Big Brother blames me?

266
00:13:01,840 --> 00:13:02,720
When the time comes,

267
00:13:03,080 --> 00:13:05,030
the four of you hit him together.

268
00:13:05,670 --> 00:13:07,200
Then he won't know who hit him.

269
00:13:07,670 --> 00:13:08,390
True.

270
00:13:22,670 --> 00:13:25,480
It's rare to see you so relaxed, Young Master.

271
00:13:25,790 --> 00:13:28,030
Joy refreshes the spirit.

272
00:13:30,150 --> 00:13:31,510
Such a beautiful night.

273
00:13:32,120 --> 00:13:33,510
Young Master, don't let it go to waste.

274
00:13:36,720 --> 00:13:38,480
A heartbroken woman...

275
00:13:38,550 --> 00:13:40,200
...needs comfort the most.

276
00:13:43,200 --> 00:13:44,270
Uncle Xiao.

277
00:13:44,840 --> 00:13:46,440
How come I never noticed before?

278
00:13:46,840 --> 00:13:48,120
That heart of yours...

279
00:13:48,240 --> 00:13:49,550
...is a bit filthy.

280
00:13:50,910 --> 00:13:53,000
Am I the kind of person who takes advantage of others?

281
00:13:54,670 --> 00:13:55,790
Of course not, Young Master.

282
00:13:57,240 --> 00:13:59,150
But Xiu Gu followed that Fan guy...

283
00:14:00,150 --> 00:14:01,030
I feel...

284
00:14:03,870 --> 00:14:04,750
...it's only fair.

285
00:14:08,000 --> 00:14:10,240
She traveled a thousand miles to find her husband.

286
00:14:10,550 --> 00:14:12,630
Only to find out her man became a bandit.

287
00:14:13,030 --> 00:14:14,360
I'm just a businessman.

288
00:14:14,440 --> 00:14:16,150
How would I know where bandits are?

289
00:14:16,720 --> 00:14:18,000
For this kind of thing...

290
00:14:18,240 --> 00:14:20,320
...she has to go find Commander Qin.

291
00:14:23,480 --> 00:14:24,200
I get it.

292
00:14:25,790 --> 00:14:26,510
First thing tomorrow morning...

293
00:14:26,720 --> 00:14:27,960
...send her over to Commander Qin.

294
00:14:28,390 --> 00:14:29,440
That guy...

295
00:14:29,630 --> 00:14:30,630
...when he sees a woman...

296
00:14:31,080 --> 00:14:32,750
...he drools enough to bruise his feet.

297
00:14:33,120 --> 00:14:35,200
We are kind-hearted.

298
00:14:35,390 --> 00:14:36,750
Helping her find her man.

299
00:14:37,320 --> 00:14:38,600
As for what happens after she finds him...

300
00:14:38,600 --> 00:14:39,870
...whatever happens...

301
00:14:40,630 --> 00:14:42,080
...has nothing to do with us.

302
00:14:42,630 --> 00:14:44,270
You really think of everything, Young Master.

303
00:14:49,270 --> 00:14:50,270
Careful.

304
00:14:53,910 --> 00:14:54,870
See that?

305
00:14:55,630 --> 00:14:56,750
When we were digging...

306
00:14:57,320 --> 00:14:59,510
...I told Xuanjizi...

307
00:14:59,840 --> 00:15:03,030
...there's a ready-made tunnel under the Huo residence.

308
00:15:04,630 --> 00:15:06,150
He just wouldn't listen.

309
00:15:06,550 --> 00:15:08,550
To prove I was right...

310
00:15:09,030 --> 00:15:11,960
...I kept digging in my original direction.

311
00:15:12,320 --> 00:15:13,960
And I actually dug through.

312
00:15:18,030 --> 00:15:18,750
Remember this.

313
00:15:19,630 --> 00:15:21,000
Never try to be a hero.

314
00:15:21,440 --> 00:15:23,000
And don't act on impulse.

315
00:15:23,240 --> 00:15:23,960
Got it.

316
00:15:26,480 --> 00:15:27,510
From now on...

317
00:15:27,790 --> 00:15:29,600
...listen to everything I say.

318
00:15:37,480 --> 00:15:39,720
You called me back? Let's keep drinking!

319
00:15:40,270 --> 00:15:41,000
Didn't you ask me...

320
00:15:41,000 --> 00:15:42,320
...why I came back?

321
00:15:42,870 --> 00:15:45,910
I came back mainly to say goodbye to you.

322
00:15:47,440 --> 00:15:48,440
Goodbye?

323
00:15:48,790 --> 00:15:49,750
You don't want to leave.

324
00:15:50,150 --> 00:15:51,600
And I don't want to stay here.

325
00:15:51,790 --> 00:15:54,000
Fine, to each their own.

326
00:15:56,030 --> 00:15:57,080
We are brothers.

327
00:15:57,440 --> 00:15:59,120
Brothers for life.

328
00:15:59,840 --> 00:16:01,390
I'll count one, two, three.

329
00:16:01,390 --> 00:16:02,550
We down a bowl.

330
00:16:02,630 --> 00:16:03,120
Okay.

331
00:16:03,390 --> 00:16:05,480
One, two, three.

332
00:16:05,600 --> 00:16:06,360
Cheers.

333
00:16:19,630 --> 00:16:20,870
There's something...

334
00:16:21,670 --> 00:16:23,200
...I've always wanted to tell you.

335
00:16:23,720 --> 00:16:24,270
Say it.

336
00:16:25,670 --> 00:16:28,790
Let's drink a bowl to build up courage.

337
00:16:29,030 --> 00:16:29,750
Okay.

338
00:16:31,200 --> 00:16:31,790
One.

339
00:16:32,120 --> 00:16:32,840
Two.

340
00:16:33,030 --> 00:16:33,750
Three.

341
00:16:34,030 --> 00:16:34,790
Cheers.

342
00:16:40,120 --> 00:16:41,150
That thing is...

343
00:16:41,910 --> 00:16:43,550
...you are so tall.

344
00:16:47,720 --> 00:16:48,600
I...

345
00:16:49,270 --> 00:16:51,630
...have one more thing to tell you.

346
00:16:51,790 --> 00:16:52,720
Say it.

347
00:16:58,000 --> 00:16:59,910
Uncle Xiao, bring a bucket of water.

348
00:17:00,150 --> 00:17:01,510
Not sleeping in the middle of the night.

349
00:17:03,670 --> 00:17:05,150
Go back. Let's rethink this.

350
00:17:09,510 --> 00:17:10,590
He left, right?

351
00:17:11,000 --> 00:17:11,480
Go up.

352
00:17:12,680 --> 00:17:13,830
Go up where?

353
00:17:14,640 --> 00:17:16,440
I was locked upstairs last time.

354
00:17:28,830 --> 00:17:29,880
There are guards.

355
00:17:30,240 --> 00:17:30,920
Retreat.

356
00:17:31,270 --> 00:17:32,070
Let's rethink this.

357
00:17:32,590 --> 00:17:34,160
Just one person, easy to deal with.

358
00:17:34,920 --> 00:17:35,920
Go back.

359
00:17:36,400 --> 00:17:37,720
Xiu Gu, go back.

360
00:17:47,590 --> 00:17:49,070
You've said eight sentences already.

361
00:17:49,590 --> 00:17:50,750
How much more do you have?

362
00:17:51,270 --> 00:17:52,720
Can't you finish it all at once?

363
00:17:53,270 --> 00:17:53,920
Alright.

364
00:17:55,480 --> 00:17:57,160
The last sentence.

365
00:17:57,160 --> 00:17:58,880
I'll count one, two, three.

366
00:17:58,880 --> 00:17:59,590
Okay.

367
00:18:01,920 --> 00:18:04,640
One, two, three.

368
00:18:18,640 --> 00:18:19,510
I know

369
00:18:20,240 --> 00:18:21,830
what you're planning with him.

370
00:18:23,880 --> 00:18:25,030
But I didn't expect

371
00:18:25,640 --> 00:18:26,880
that the four of you

372
00:18:27,400 --> 00:18:29,510
would follow them too.

373
00:18:30,110 --> 00:18:31,350
I expected even less

374
00:18:32,160 --> 00:18:33,680
that you would be the leader.

375
00:18:33,680 --> 00:18:36,270
Ma the Tigress is ruthless.

376
00:18:36,750 --> 00:18:38,240
She'll stop at nothing to get what she wants.

377
00:18:38,640 --> 00:18:39,510
She's temperamental.

378
00:18:39,750 --> 00:18:41,270
We all live in constant fear.

379
00:18:41,510 --> 00:18:43,070
Brother Scarface barely escaped with his life.

380
00:18:43,160 --> 00:18:44,510
He is a warning to us all.

381
00:18:45,440 --> 00:18:46,440
Most importantly,

382
00:18:46,830 --> 00:18:48,680
you'll never be her husband

383
00:18:48,680 --> 00:18:49,750
or rise to power.

384
00:18:50,070 --> 00:18:51,000
How can our lives as brothers

385
00:18:51,000 --> 00:18:52,680
possibly be carefree and happy?

386
00:19:07,160 --> 00:19:08,830
Why don't the two of us just leave?

387
00:19:12,200 --> 00:19:12,920
Big Brother,

388
00:19:35,000 --> 00:19:36,350
no key.

389
00:19:37,160 --> 00:19:38,790
Retreat. Let's rethink this.

390
00:19:45,350 --> 00:19:46,240
Keep it down.

391
00:19:50,590 --> 00:19:51,350
Who?

392
00:19:51,720 --> 00:19:52,720
Who is it?

393
00:19:53,110 --> 00:19:53,960
Mrs. Fan,

394
00:19:54,240 --> 00:19:55,400
we're here to rescue you.

395
00:20:04,640 --> 00:20:05,590
Mrs. Fan.

396
00:20:07,270 --> 00:20:07,960
You are...

397
00:20:07,960 --> 00:20:08,960
I am Xiu Gu,

398
00:20:09,880 --> 00:20:10,920
Brother Fan's friend.

399
00:20:11,750 --> 00:20:12,640
My name is Yu Zhen.

400
00:20:12,790 --> 00:20:13,440
Sister Yu Zhen.

401
00:20:14,160 --> 00:20:15,550
That Young Master Huo isn't a good person.

402
00:20:15,720 --> 00:20:16,830
Come with us.

403
00:20:19,440 --> 00:20:20,510
That Young Master Huo said

404
00:20:20,640 --> 00:20:22,110
he was sworn brothers with my husband,

405
00:20:22,880 --> 00:20:24,000
but he locked me up here.

406
00:20:24,750 --> 00:20:26,750
Now you say you're my husband's friend.

407
00:20:27,480 --> 00:20:28,000
I don't know

408
00:20:28,000 --> 00:20:29,270
where you want to take me.

409
00:20:29,720 --> 00:20:30,880
How can I trust you?

410
00:20:32,550 --> 00:20:33,720
She doesn't trust you.

411
00:20:33,720 --> 00:20:34,920
She won't go with you.

412
00:20:35,110 --> 00:20:36,790
Retreat. Let's rethink this.

413
00:20:39,590 --> 00:20:40,550
Brother Fan said

414
00:20:41,030 --> 00:20:42,440
you're prone to boils.

415
00:20:43,550 --> 00:20:45,160
Sister Yu Zhen, come with us.

416
00:20:45,240 --> 00:20:45,880
Someone fainted!

417
00:20:45,920 --> 00:20:46,880
Help!

418
00:20:47,030 --> 00:20:47,590
Help!

419
00:20:47,590 --> 00:20:48,920
Come with us. Hurry!

420
00:20:48,920 --> 00:20:50,160
Help! Someone come quick!

421
00:20:54,000 --> 00:20:54,640
This way.

422
00:20:59,110 --> 00:21:00,790
Quick! Quick! Chase them! Chase them!

423
00:21:01,000 --> 00:21:01,750
Go!

424
00:21:04,920 --> 00:21:05,510
Quick!

425
00:21:10,920 --> 00:21:11,790
Hurry up! Hurry!

426
00:21:20,440 --> 00:21:21,160
Turn left!

427
00:21:28,590 --> 00:21:29,160
Go, go, go!

428
00:21:33,960 --> 00:21:35,070
Chase them!

429
00:21:35,240 --> 00:21:36,110
Stop! Stop!

430
00:21:36,790 --> 00:21:37,400
Chase them!

431
00:21:38,070 --> 00:21:38,640
Go!

432
00:21:39,030 --> 00:21:40,030
Stop right there!

433
00:21:41,070 --> 00:21:41,590
Run!

434
00:21:41,790 --> 00:21:42,750
Where do you think you're going?

435
00:21:43,680 --> 00:21:44,480
Stop!

436
00:21:45,200 --> 00:21:45,790
Stop!

437
00:21:46,310 --> 00:21:46,960
Stop!

438
00:21:47,640 --> 00:21:48,200
Stop!

439
00:21:50,880 --> 00:21:52,200
Stop right there!

440
00:21:52,960 --> 00:21:54,400
Stop! Stop!

441
00:22:02,400 --> 00:22:04,680
You'll never get away!

442
00:22:15,240 --> 00:22:16,640
How come it's you?

443
00:22:19,480 --> 00:22:20,070
After him!

444
00:22:20,880 --> 00:22:21,640
Hurry up!

445
00:22:27,000 --> 00:22:28,400
Uncle Dong.

446
00:22:29,790 --> 00:22:31,830
You have disappointed me greatly.

447
00:22:32,590 --> 00:22:33,720
You father and daughter...

448
00:22:33,880 --> 00:22:36,350
...have completely disregarded our families' friendship.

449
00:22:36,720 --> 00:22:37,920
You insist on opposing me.

450
00:22:39,750 --> 00:22:42,480
It is my son-in-law who gave me this confidence.

451
00:22:43,400 --> 00:22:44,160
What?

452
00:22:45,480 --> 00:22:46,480
Son-in-law?

453
00:22:47,830 --> 00:22:50,440
What kind of magic does that Fan guy have?

454
00:22:50,720 --> 00:22:52,510
He doesn't have any magic.

455
00:22:53,350 --> 00:22:55,110
It's just that his appearance...

456
00:22:55,310 --> 00:22:57,830
...has made me see many things clearly.

457
00:23:01,350 --> 00:23:03,550
Including seeing you clearly.

458
00:23:07,160 --> 00:23:08,000
People...

459
00:23:08,510 --> 00:23:09,960
...really fear comparison.

460
00:23:13,830 --> 00:23:15,000
You mean...

461
00:23:15,920 --> 00:23:17,000
...I'm not as good as him?

462
00:23:23,000 --> 00:23:23,880
Find a place.

463
00:23:24,750 --> 00:23:25,640
Get rid of him.

464
00:23:27,750 --> 00:23:28,720
What are you saying?

465
00:23:28,920 --> 00:23:30,070
Don't make a scene.

466
00:23:31,160 --> 00:23:32,240
You dare!

467
00:23:32,400 --> 00:23:33,510
Don't you forget...

468
00:23:33,510 --> 00:23:35,110
...I am your elder.

469
00:23:35,240 --> 00:23:36,400
Do it.

470
00:23:36,400 --> 00:23:38,160
I watched you grow up!

471
00:23:38,480 --> 00:23:39,790
Which of you dares?

472
00:23:40,440 --> 00:23:40,920
Tie him up.

473
00:23:41,960 --> 00:23:42,550
You...

474
00:23:42,590 --> 00:23:44,030
What are you doing?

475
00:23:44,240 --> 00:23:44,750
Move!

476
00:23:44,920 --> 00:23:46,110
What are you doing?

477
00:23:46,680 --> 00:23:48,480
What on earth are you doing?

478
00:23:51,680 --> 00:23:53,510
I don't need anyone...

479
00:23:54,000 --> 00:23:55,350
...to be compared with me.

480
00:23:58,110 --> 00:23:59,270
Ma the Tigress!

481
00:24:00,000 --> 00:24:02,000
Ma the Tigress! Get the hell out here!

482
00:24:02,000 --> 00:24:03,030
Ma the Tigress!

483
00:24:09,270 --> 00:24:10,200
Do it then.

484
00:24:11,480 --> 00:24:12,680
I beg you to kill me.

485
00:24:13,680 --> 00:24:15,270
To die in your hands...

486
00:24:16,310 --> 00:24:17,590
...I am willing.

487
00:24:17,920 --> 00:24:19,310
Don't act like a drunk here.

488
00:24:20,590 --> 00:24:22,590
Why are you so cold to me?

489
00:24:24,240 --> 00:24:25,240
Out of everyone...

490
00:24:25,240 --> 00:24:26,960
...I am the most loyal to you.

491
00:24:27,590 --> 00:24:29,680
Why can't you just look at me once more?

492
00:24:36,270 --> 00:24:37,070
I know.

493
00:24:38,000 --> 00:24:39,110
You are the most obedient.

494
00:24:39,720 --> 00:24:41,200
Then you need to make everyone...

495
00:24:41,550 --> 00:24:42,720
...be just like you...

496
00:24:43,400 --> 00:24:44,480
...and be loyal to me.

497
00:24:45,240 --> 00:24:47,200
That is the best way for you to love me.

498
00:24:49,270 --> 00:24:51,270
I've always wanted to help you.

499
00:24:52,750 --> 00:24:54,790
I want everyone to submit to you.

500
00:24:56,070 --> 00:24:57,550
But I'm also conflicted.

501
00:24:58,680 --> 00:25:00,720
I don't want others getting close to you.

502
00:25:01,440 --> 00:25:02,750
I don't want others...

503
00:25:02,960 --> 00:25:04,590
...to take away your love for me.

504
00:25:08,070 --> 00:25:09,000
Don't worry.

505
00:25:09,680 --> 00:25:11,680
You will always be my one and only Big Brother.

506
00:25:12,350 --> 00:25:13,400
Then why...

507
00:25:14,110 --> 00:25:16,550
...did you appoint a strategist above me?

508
00:25:16,680 --> 00:25:18,030
My patience is limited.

509
00:25:19,550 --> 00:25:20,350
Look at you.

510
00:25:20,920 --> 00:25:23,000
As soon as he's mentioned, you get like this.

511
00:25:23,240 --> 00:25:24,550
What's so good about him?

512
00:25:25,790 --> 00:25:27,960
He thinks of ways to leave here every day.

513
00:25:28,070 --> 00:25:29,440
And drags me along too.

514
00:25:29,880 --> 00:25:30,720
He wants to leave?

515
00:25:31,270 --> 00:25:32,830
I'll call him over for you right now.

516
00:25:33,720 --> 00:25:35,200
Ask him to his face.

517
00:25:37,240 --> 00:25:40,110
I'll call him over right away.

518
00:25:48,400 --> 00:25:49,110
What is it?

519
00:25:49,830 --> 00:25:50,750
What's with you?

520
00:25:53,550 --> 00:25:54,400
Ma the Tigress.

521
00:25:56,270 --> 00:25:57,790
What's going on?

522
00:25:58,920 --> 00:26:00,070
Since he came here...

523
00:26:00,510 --> 00:26:01,480
...how have I treated him?

524
00:26:01,590 --> 00:26:02,590
You've treated me very well.

525
00:26:02,750 --> 00:26:03,440
I'm talking about him.

526
00:26:04,070 --> 00:26:05,720
Ma the Tigress made him Advisor.

527
00:26:06,240 --> 00:26:07,200
Accompanied him on missions.

528
00:26:07,480 --> 00:26:08,640
Doted on him.

529
00:26:09,240 --> 00:26:10,720
The brothers have all seen it.

530
00:26:10,960 --> 00:26:13,270
I made you second only to me.

531
00:26:13,880 --> 00:26:14,960
I haven't treated you badly.

532
00:26:15,440 --> 00:26:18,200
You treat me like a brother, like a parent.

533
00:26:18,440 --> 00:26:19,590
Then why do you still want to leave?

534
00:26:21,200 --> 00:26:21,790
Leave.

535
00:26:23,480 --> 00:26:24,200
Leave.

536
00:26:24,510 --> 00:26:25,720
Leave.

537
00:26:26,000 --> 00:26:27,070
It's all for you.

538
00:26:29,510 --> 00:26:30,310
For me?

539
00:26:32,400 --> 00:26:33,880
My condition of fainting at the sight of blood...

540
00:26:34,310 --> 00:26:36,590
I didn't know it was so serious before.

541
00:26:37,240 --> 00:26:39,720
You took us down the mountain on so many missions.

542
00:26:40,200 --> 00:26:42,270
You were so mighty and heroic.

543
00:26:44,440 --> 00:26:46,750
But I'm just holding you back.

544
00:26:48,350 --> 00:26:49,720
You're such a smooth talker.

545
00:26:51,110 --> 00:26:52,310
What's the problem with that?

546
00:26:52,640 --> 00:26:54,200
You don't have to go on missions anymore.

547
00:26:55,920 --> 00:26:59,270
Not going on missions means I'm a freeloader.

548
00:27:00,310 --> 00:27:02,160
I might as well just leave.

549
00:27:03,960 --> 00:27:05,000
Besides missions...

550
00:27:05,200 --> 00:27:06,960
...there are plenty of other things to do.

551
00:27:07,350 --> 00:27:08,440
I won't let you go.

552
00:27:09,510 --> 00:27:10,720
No one will dare object.

553
00:27:17,550 --> 00:27:19,240
Filial piety comes first.

554
00:27:19,680 --> 00:27:21,960
I mainly want to go back and see my parents.

555
00:27:22,480 --> 00:27:23,200
Who are you kidding?

556
00:27:23,440 --> 00:27:25,070
Your parents died long ago.

557
00:27:27,550 --> 00:27:28,590
I haven't finished.

558
00:27:29,400 --> 00:27:31,960
I want to visit my parents' graves.

559
00:27:32,310 --> 00:27:33,830
And burn some incense for them.

560
00:27:34,750 --> 00:27:35,640
That's simple.

561
00:27:36,070 --> 00:27:37,270
I'll send ten brothers.

562
00:27:37,510 --> 00:27:38,790
To go back with you.

563
00:27:39,000 --> 00:27:40,030
Ten isn't enough.

564
00:27:40,510 --> 00:27:41,480
Then twenty.

565
00:27:41,590 --> 00:27:43,200
So you can show off...

566
00:27:43,510 --> 00:27:44,640
...in front of your parents.

567
00:27:47,070 --> 00:27:49,310
I do have a selfish motive.

568
00:27:49,480 --> 00:27:50,030
Go on.

569
00:27:51,830 --> 00:27:53,590
I want to go back and see my wife.

570
00:27:55,350 --> 00:27:56,400
You know, Yu Zhen.

571
00:27:57,550 --> 00:27:59,110
Think about it, I've been away so long.

572
00:27:59,880 --> 00:28:01,720
Yu Zhen doesn't know my situation.

573
00:28:02,200 --> 00:28:03,400
What if she runs off...

574
00:28:03,790 --> 00:28:05,110
...with someone else?

575
00:28:06,310 --> 00:28:08,070
You really are a romantic.

576
00:28:08,750 --> 00:28:10,110
When the soldiers ease up,

577
00:28:10,720 --> 00:28:12,110
I'll personally go back with you.

578
00:28:12,240 --> 00:28:13,400
To see your wife.

579
00:28:14,240 --> 00:28:15,680
If she has run off with someone else,

580
00:28:16,240 --> 00:28:17,750
I'll personally help you get revenge.

581
00:28:19,750 --> 00:28:20,960
Anything else you want to make up?

582
00:28:21,960 --> 00:28:22,590
That's it.

583
00:28:23,310 --> 00:28:24,240
I can't make up anything else.

584
00:28:28,070 --> 00:28:29,680
Then stay here quietly.

585
00:28:30,270 --> 00:28:30,830
Alright.

586
00:28:36,480 --> 00:28:37,110
Will your dad...

587
00:28:37,270 --> 00:28:38,640
...have trouble finding us?

588
00:28:38,720 --> 00:28:39,310
No.

589
00:28:39,440 --> 00:28:40,400
I arranged it with him.

590
00:28:40,400 --> 00:28:41,310
To meet right here.

591
00:28:46,000 --> 00:28:48,160
My husband and Young Master Huo...

592
00:28:48,750 --> 00:28:50,550
...what deep grudge is there between them?

593
00:28:54,830 --> 00:28:56,270
Mainly...

594
00:28:57,680 --> 00:28:58,680
Because of me.

595
00:29:01,750 --> 00:29:04,350
I say, what exactly are you doing?

596
00:29:04,830 --> 00:29:06,240
I just took a girl...

597
00:29:06,350 --> 00:29:07,510
...from your house.

598
00:29:07,590 --> 00:29:09,920
That shouldn't be a crime.

599
00:29:11,440 --> 00:29:12,880
Even if it is a crime,

600
00:29:13,070 --> 00:29:15,110
You can't take the law into your own hands.

601
00:29:15,920 --> 00:29:17,550
And do whatever you please.

602
00:29:17,720 --> 00:29:18,480
Uncle Dong.

603
00:29:18,880 --> 00:29:21,440
If you had just peacefully let Xiu Gu...

604
00:29:21,960 --> 00:29:23,200
...marry into our Huo Family...

605
00:29:24,000 --> 00:29:25,240
...it wouldn't have come to this.

606
00:29:25,880 --> 00:29:27,440
Today, it's not that I want to kill you.

607
00:29:27,920 --> 00:29:29,960
Nor does our Young Master want to kill you.

608
00:29:30,640 --> 00:29:32,000
You brought this on yourself.

609
00:29:32,270 --> 00:29:34,110
Today, for the sake of old times...

610
00:29:36,350 --> 00:29:37,160
No, no, no! Don't! Don't!

611
00:29:37,160 --> 00:29:38,240
I'll make it quick.

612
00:29:38,590 --> 00:29:39,160
Don't!

613
00:29:40,720 --> 00:29:42,350
Xiu Gu!

614
00:29:42,920 --> 00:29:45,510
Run! Run as far as you can!

615
00:29:45,920 --> 00:29:47,640
Don't ever...

616
00:29:49,000 --> 00:29:50,310
...come back!

617
00:29:50,750 --> 00:29:51,880
Dad!

618
00:29:53,240 --> 00:29:54,200
Dad!

619
00:29:55,200 --> 00:29:55,750
After them!

620
00:30:42,000 --> 00:30:42,960
Where are we

621
00:30:43,350 --> 00:30:44,270
going now?

622
00:30:44,440 --> 00:30:45,110
The bandit den.

623
00:30:45,590 --> 00:30:46,590
The bandit den?

624
00:30:47,750 --> 00:30:49,750
Everyone in town says Brother Fan went up the mountain.

625
00:30:50,160 --> 00:30:51,030
I'm going to find him.

626
00:30:51,680 --> 00:30:53,240
He will definitely avenge my father.

627
00:30:54,270 --> 00:30:56,240
Young Master Huo is rich and powerful.

628
00:30:56,720 --> 00:30:57,790
Brother Fan is all alone.

629
00:30:58,350 --> 00:30:59,200
He's just one man.

630
00:30:59,440 --> 00:31:00,720
How can he avenge you?

631
00:31:01,590 --> 00:31:03,510
The Brother Fan I know can take on a hundred men.

632
00:31:04,070 --> 00:31:05,240
I believe he can do it.

633
00:31:07,720 --> 00:31:08,720
I don't believe Brother Fan

634
00:31:09,160 --> 00:31:10,240
would become a bandit.

635
00:31:13,200 --> 00:31:14,790
Why don't you go back first?

636
00:31:15,750 --> 00:31:16,960
Once I find Brother Fan,

637
00:31:17,440 --> 00:31:18,680
I'll tell him you were here.

638
00:31:21,880 --> 00:31:22,960
Come with me.

639
00:31:23,310 --> 00:31:24,440
Let's go back to Weiyuan together.

640
00:31:24,750 --> 00:31:25,440
Back to the Fan house.

641
00:31:25,830 --> 00:31:27,400
We'll tell Great-Uncle what happened here.

642
00:31:28,160 --> 00:31:29,480
He is highly respected.

643
00:31:30,000 --> 00:31:31,680
He'll surely help us find a way.

644
00:31:32,200 --> 00:31:33,070
This isn't Weiyuan.

645
00:31:33,070 --> 00:31:34,000
There's no Fan house here.

646
00:31:34,000 --> 00:31:35,440
And no Great-Uncle of yours.

647
00:31:36,830 --> 00:31:38,000
This is the deep wilderness.

648
00:31:38,720 --> 00:31:40,720
Here, there are only lost paths and no way home.

649
00:31:40,720 --> 00:31:41,750
Here, my father died,

650
00:31:41,750 --> 00:31:43,400
and I can't even retrieve his body.

651
00:31:50,720 --> 00:31:51,750
Sister Yu Zhen,

652
00:31:53,350 --> 00:31:55,240
I don't have a father anymore.

653
00:31:57,750 --> 00:32:00,110
I've lost my father.

654
00:32:07,640 --> 00:32:09,510
I'm going to find Brother Fan.

655
00:32:11,000 --> 00:32:12,790
He can definitely help me.

656
00:32:14,270 --> 00:32:15,110
Are you sure

657
00:32:15,480 --> 00:32:16,680
Brother Fan went up the mountain?

658
00:32:16,960 --> 00:32:18,240
Even if it's just a rumor,

659
00:32:19,510 --> 00:32:20,750
I have to try.

660
00:32:21,200 --> 00:32:22,200
Then I'll go with you.

661
00:32:24,110 --> 00:32:25,240
It's a bandit den.

662
00:32:26,200 --> 00:32:27,550
You don't need to risk your life with me.

663
00:32:27,960 --> 00:32:28,790
You and your father

664
00:32:29,000 --> 00:32:29,960
risked your lives to save me.

665
00:32:30,960 --> 00:32:32,110
I won't leave you behind.

666
00:32:32,830 --> 00:32:33,400
Don't move!

667
00:32:37,830 --> 00:32:39,030
Move! Come up the mountain with us.
